course_info.trial_description:
A Trial Lesson is available to understand students' needs and goals. During this lesson, we get to know each other and look to see whether we work well together. We will also discuss your main learning difficulties. In addition to this, I may determine your level through a short test.

The free trial lesson lasts 30 minutes and consists of the following parts:

Introductions and short dialogue;
Questions about the level and difficulties of the student;
Student’s questions about the education and experience of the teacher.

